{"tid":2046253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口交部終於回應：美國犯法","createTime":"2020-06-01T09:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T11:36:52.000Z","uid":125168,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"630634a862a0ccbb9bd0adf8bc8bd7c7240c7b22","tid":2046253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"中方批美國就港區國安法施制裁嚴重干涉內政違背國際法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392944&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns89qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=caaa2dad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392944&h=ac1d8245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392944</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在北京，外交部稱，堅決反對美國就中方制定港區國安法實施制裁行動，批評美方指摘罔顧事實，警告美方這樣做，嚴重干涉中國內政及違背國際法。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人趙立堅：「美方領導人對中方的種種指摘，完全罔顧事實，所宣布的措施嚴重干涉中國內政，破壞中美關係，必將損人害己，中方對此堅決反對。香港是中國的香港，香港事務純屬中國內政，任何外國對此都無權干涉，也不應干涉；中國政府維護國家主權、安全發展利益的決心堅定不移，貫徹一國兩制方針的決心堅定不移，反對任何外部勢力違法干預香港事務的決心堅定不移；美方對香港國家安全立法橫加干涉，完全違背國際法和國際關係基本準則，是注定要失敗的。」"},{"pid":"dca7a27aca383876490dae09629008f1c7192b51","tid":2046253,"uid":125168,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:35:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母南海撤撚咗未呀學人講國際法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a009604b660a15facce264e1bacfa9741d953b9f","tid":2046253,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b120b16a94254b6d9910a8866bc2ce89e5611ed0","tid":2046253,"uid":59408,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"告上國際法庭<br />\n快<br />\n唔做正契弟<br />\n<br />\